# Slide with Standard Configuration

This slide uses the global configuration defined in the FrontMatter:
- Header: "Standard Configuration" (center)
- Footer: "Advanced Corp" (left) + "December 27, 2024" (right) + "2 / 12" (right)

This is the **base** configuration applied by default to all `content`-type slides.

