# Configuration Methods

::: info
**Global (FrontMatter)**
- ✅ Easy to maintain
- ✅ Guaranteed consistency
- ❌ Less flexibility
- ❌ One configuration for everything
- **Ideal for:** Standard presentations
:::

::: success
**Per Layout** ⭐ **Recommended**
- ✅ Contextual configuration
- ✅ Medium flexibility
- ✅ Reasonable maintenance
- ✅ Better user experience
- **Ideal for:** Professional presentations
:::

::: warning
**Per Individual Slide**
- ✅ Maximum granular control
- ✅ Total customization
- ❌ More configuration work
- ❌ Complex maintenance
- **Ideal for:** Special specific slides
:::

