# Per-Slide Implementation

This is how a specific override is configured:

```yaml
---
layout: content
header:
  text:
    content: "My Custom Header"
    color: "#ff6b6b"
    position: "left"
footer:
  page_numbers:
    format: "Page {{current}} of {{total}}"
    prefix: "📄 "
  text:
    left: "Specific information"
    center: "Only for this slide"
    right: "Override active"
---

# My Custom Slide
Normal slide content...
```

**Configurable elements per slide:**
- Header text (content, color, position, style)
- Page numbers (format, prefix, suffix)
- Footer text (left, center, right)
- Enabled state (enabled: true/false)

