# Use Cases for Overrides

## Confidential Slides
Red headers, footers with security warnings

## Real-Time Dashboards
Headers with timestamp, footers with system status

## Special Sections
Headers with section name, contextual footers

## Demo Slides
Headers indicating "DEMO", footers with disclaimers

## Multi-Language Presentations
Headers/footers in a specific language per slide

