# Implementation Process

## 1. 📋 Base Configuration
Define global header/footer in FrontMatter

## 2. 🎯 Identify Special Slides
Mark slides that need specific configuration

## 3. ⚙️ Apply Overrides
Add YAML configuration for specific slides

## 4. ✅ Validate and Adjust
Review the final result and adjust as needed

